					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="640" height="424" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-81.png" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-81.png?w=640&amp;ssl=1 640w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-81.png?resize=220%2C146&amp;ssl=1 220w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
