		<title>狗狗「翻肚肚」給人摸＝撒嬌？真相可能更複雜 !</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/06/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e3%80%8c%e7%bf%bb%e8%82%9a%e8%82%9a%e3%80%8d%e7%b5%a6%e4%ba%ba%e6%91%b8%ef%bc%9d%e6%92%92%e5%ac%8c%ef%bc%9f%e7%9c%9f%e7%9b%b8%e5%8f%af%e8%83%bd%e6%9b%b4%e8%a4%87%e9%9b%9c/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sun, 06 Jul 2025 06:58:11 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
